nodes.text: Jedi Master Quinlan Vos amassed a spy network within the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Separatist Crisis of 24 to 22 BBY. He was aided in its creation by Master Tholme.
His agents were unable to predict the Battle of Geonosis; however, in the Mission to The Wheel, they were able to get information on the impending attack on Kamino.
